<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/elite-style.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-card">
            <div class="login-form">
                <div class="form-header">
                    <h1>404
                        <span>Elite Business Edition</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p>页面未找到</p>
                </div>
                <p style="text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; color: var(--text-secondary);">您访问的页面不存在或已被移除。</p>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-block" id="back-home-btn">
                    <i class="fas fa-home"></i> 返回首页
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="login-info">
                <div class="info-header">
                    <h2>错误信息</h2>
                    <p>您尝试访问的页面可能已被删除、移动或输入了错误的URL地址。</p>
                </div>
                <ul class="info-features">
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-check"></i>
                        <span>检查URL地址是否正确</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-history"></i>
                        <span>使用浏览器历史记录返回</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-home"></i>
                        <span>返回首页重新导航</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                        <span>使用搜索功能查找内容</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
